'''Desset Fabien''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed the [[Pitrillistian]]s and [[Pitrillistia]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the 16-years-and-older category. He was 19 at the time his entry was published.

